<h2 class="bold font-l">LazyTown - My Grocery List</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In &quot;Rottenbeard&quot; from &quot;LazyTown,&quot; Robbie Rotten poses as a pirate named Rottenbeard to lead the children of LazyTown on a treasure hunt. Thing is, his treasure map is a list reading &quot;Paper towels, milk, chocolate covered anchovies.&quot; Oh wait... that's his grocery list. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OhWaitThisIsMyGroceryList" class='trope-example-link'>Oh Wait, This Is My Grocery List</a></p>
